ger of Allah, which deed is best?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFaith in Allah and jihad in His way.\u201d I said, \u201cWhich slave is the best to free?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cOne who is valuable to his\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13995,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/06\/every-step-mosque-rewarded\/","url_meta":{"origin":22398,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Mosques: Every step to mosque for prayer is rewarded","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever purifies himself with ablution in his house, then he walks to a house among the houses of Allah to fulfill an obligation among the obligations of Allah, one step of his will expiate his sins\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42588,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/02\/counted-every-step\/","url_meta":{"origin":22398,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Masjid: Allah counted every step as a reward","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 2, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ubayy ibn Ka\u2019b reported: There was a man who lived the furthest from the mosque, as far as I know. He never missed a congregational prayer. It was said to him, \u201cIf you buy a donkey, you can ride it during the dark nights and hot days.\u201d The man said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28614,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/01\/salat-nawafil-at-home\/","url_meta":{"origin":22398,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Perform voluntary prayers at home","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 1, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen one of you finishes the prayer in his mosque, let him perform a portion of his prayer in his house. Verily, Allah will bring about good from his prayer in his house.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 778\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7195,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/25\/best-masjid-worst-suq-aswaq\/","url_meta":{"origin":22398,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Masajid: Best places are mosques, worst are markets","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 25, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe most beloved of places to Allah are the mosques, and the most hated of places to Allah are the markets.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 671 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \